body:
Sound effects from <Bad to the Bone>'s riff when killing Skeletons/Wither Skeletons/Skeletons.

Precautions:
- The resource pack **doesn't include** the entire song "Bad to the Bone" in the game, it **only adds** the sound effect of the "dududa-dududa" riff;
- I **don't know** what your thoughts are about this song/the resource pack, _as long as you're happy_;
- _~~Skeletons are so bad!~~_
